css contains three types 
inline,internal,external
inline means single line css this is also key vale pairs 
internal means same hyml page la thaniya style tag la nama css kudutha internal
div tag contains the in html that can take height.html laa iruka condunt iruka varikum heigth set panikum
athee css la div kududthu height set panikala athu panum pothu fixed aa tha work aagum
external css na thaniya oru css create pani athaa html la link pananum
<link real ="style.css"href="style.css //path"
css selectors
element,class,id,universal
element means h1,p individual
class means create a class in html and css putting dot .and value 
id means putting # symbol before the class value id name must be 
only one but class are repated created same valueor name

universal means * it covers the hole html page 
css box model margin,borders,padding,content

content nama kudukura content ,padding top-left-right-bottom naa nama kudukura
content la irunthu chages aagum 
margin na athu mela margin irunthu work aagum
border na 3 kadipa venum border color,style, width
text-align centern na center la varum

display property inline ,inline block,block,none
inline na athu vanthu element ooda size evalavo athu varikum dha work aagum but block na
full eduthukum inline-block na athu same as inline but height and widht nama pana mudium
